# Dashboard
![Image Alt](file:///C:/Users/Versha/Pictures/Screenshots/swiggy%20dashboard.png)

## Overview

The dashboard provides a visual representation of the insights derived from the Swiggy dataset. It was built using Microsoft Excel charts and pivot tables to allow quick understanding of food ordering trends.

## Dashboard Components

• Total restaurants and dishes analyzed
• Popular food categories
• Top-rated restaurants
• Price distribution of dishes
• Customer rating trends

## Purpose

The dashboard helps users easily interpret the data by presenting important metrics in a visual and interactive format.

## Visualization Tools

Microsoft Excel charts
Pivot charts
Data filters and slicers

The dashboard allows users to quickly explore patterns in customer preferences, restaurant performance, and food pricing trends.



